All Implemented Interfaces:
HierarchicalStringObjectMap<ListHierarchyNode<Map<String,Object>>>, HierarchyNode<Map<String,Object>,ListHierarchyNode<Map<String,Object>>>, Serializable, Iterable<ListHierarchyNode<Map<String,Object>>>, Map<String,Object>
public class BasicHierarchicalStringObjectMap
extends ListHierarchyNode<Map<String,Object>>
implements HierarchicalStringObjectMap<ListHierarchyNode<Map<String,Object>>>

A node in a simple hierarchy, where a Map from Strings to Objects is attached at each node. Implements the Map interface and simply delegates to the contained Map. The children are stored in a List and are thus ordered.
